                     <interp inst="t17750426-23-person262" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am servant to Mr. Layton, a pawnbroker. This pair of tea tongs' and these three rings, (producing them) I took in of the prisoner, and lent him ten shillings upon them.</p>
               <p>They are deposed to by Mrs. Lawson.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17750426-23-person263">
                  John
                   Brooks
               <interp inst="t17750426-23-person263" type="surname" value="Brooks"></interp>
